conformance.naming

Class NamingTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • test.Test
      • conformance.naming.NamingTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContactTest, CreationTest, ListingTest, RegistrationTest, StubRetrievalTest

    abstract class NamingTest
extends Test
    Base class of naming server tests.

    On initialization, this class starts a naming server and creates stubs for its service and registration interfaces. These objects are then accessible to subclasses of NamingTest.

    Derived classes should override testServer to include the main test code. Derived classes should override initialize and clean if they have additional servers or system objects to create, start, stop, and clean up.
